{"tid":1892550,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來連阿姐都唔睇CCTVB新聞，反而睇有線新聞","createTime":"2020-02-22T15:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T23:20:57.000Z","uid":35221,"like":713,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"332bd468df2377de5c54dd99c83268f62def8f01","tid":1892550,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"【連阿姐都...】汪明荃翻攝有線新聞畫面 網民驚訝：唔睇TVB?<br />\n<br />\n22/2/2020<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/IQ7MbOQQfg34Hn3h2p4agm-bt4U=/412x231/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/7USD3RJWANAHNS5NXTK7PVAQS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FIQ7MbOQQfg34Hn3h2p4agm-bt4U%3D%2F412x231%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F7USD3RJWANAHNS5NXTK7PVAQS4.jpg&h=1969cc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ZzfabqR8kbARNAUfVEa4Y531FuI=/412x508/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/LOOVONY2ATBAK4X6ASUTQECFWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FZzfabqR8kbARNAUfVEa4Y531FuI%3D%2F412x508%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FLOOVONY2ATBAK4X6ASUTQECFWI.jpg&h=222c031f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐」汪明荃自從開了IG帳戶後，經常更新動態，跟大眾分享生活點滴，昨晚她又在IG貼出一張翻攝電視新聞報道的畫面，留言：「21/02/2020歡迎立法會財委會通過抗疫基金三百億撥款申請。」阿姐自然是想表達為抗疫基金通過撥款而拍掌讚好，不過網民的重點卻落在別處。<br />\n<br />\n72歲汪阿姐服務TVB將近50年，精明的她對很多事情都看得通透，而從她選擇收看的電視台又透出多少端倪？無綫新聞台雖則免費，打開電視就24小時可以睇到，但「逆權運動」發生後就不斷被網民批評新聞報道偏頗，以前許多開着CCTVB新聞台的食肆都紛紛轉台，原來連阿姐都轉台睇有線新聞！網民紛紛留言：「連Liza姐都唔睇TVB新聞？」、「也可以睇ViuTV。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200222/23PJOM75RR3ZKLZY5UOTTN7FHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200222%2F23PJOM75RR3ZKLZY5UOTTN7FHM%2F&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=ea5494c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200222%2F23PJOM75RR3ZKLZY5UOTTN7FHM%2F&h=9a377803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200222/23PJOM75RR3ZKLZY5UOTTN7FHM/</a>"},{"pid":"b228bd32975197076ae41055289322988ae3a8cf","tid":1892550,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568e5fd9bdd8631db24ec0dee03e2c37dd6815b5","tid":1892550,"uid":288048,"like":348,"dislike":1,"score":347,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"有線好嘢嚟"},{"pid":"12bfac5bf7021cbce621c942283d1491ac5d03f2","tid":1892550,"uid":9328,"like":448,"dislike":2,"score":446,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"我都認為有線新聞係電視上係最好，好過now"},{"pid":"39ae886fd968ae1754d0e380b9adaf3898bdcfc2","tid":1892550,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c183d97d85a504ed22ccf0bcce22c3a333a7ac11","tid":1892550,"uid":199670,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"12bfac5bf7021cbce621c942283d1491ac5d03f2","tid":1892550,"uid":9328,"like":448,"dislike":2,"score":446,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"我都認為有線新聞係電視上係最好，好過now"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"f4b1ae6fad0a16261d3d7e72ccd58efd793ddf6e","tid":1892550,"uid":39514,"like":4,"dislike":59,"score":-55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"我老豆藍到仆街都睇有線新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d862c8041493e8dac761bab6db88d3ef11df256","tid":1892550,"uid":51920,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":